  "title": "Wilted Smoked Croatian Duck Legs Stew",
  "description": "This is a rich and flavorful one-pot stew from Croatia that combines the earthiness of smoked duck legs with the brightness of floral notes. It's a hearty meal that pairs well with a side of crusty bread or over egg noodles.",
